# Cycle 4 (1-2 internal): Model crowdsourced benefit - assume after 3-4 real runs (with coarse/rough logged from #7), future sim uses aggregated NVH map for pre-load rumble segments (rumbleAuxFactor boosted 1.5x in preview for known rough road like 國道).
# Predict full script #7: red -6 to -7.5, eff 1.1+, 75%+ ROAD_MID, roughness 0.8-1.2 logged, personal 1.2+, ema 2.3+, preview factor 1.4-1.6. Contrast to old baseline in same run.
# Include IMU hybrid: aux ref mix improves err sample for mid in rumble segs (Skoda 200-350 focus).
