# === HOW THIS ACCELERATES ITER ===
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== HOW THIS ACCELERATES ITER ==="
Write-Host "One real drive with strict cond (55+ rough low-music pers=1.2) + full A/B (old prep/4/4b/5 unchanged + #6/#7 new) + log newfields (rough/pers/ema/coarse) gives rich data: within-log #4b baseline vs #7 rumble contrib (IMU+personal+rough+preview deltas quantified via eff/red/dom/%ROAD_MID + newfields). Parse log (abs path), feed real stats to sim_iter.ps1 (update calib in C3/C4 funcs or re-exec), sim re-predicts next gains + crowd NVH preload factors from logged coarse/rough clusters (e.g. 國道 rough segs -> future 1.15x aux). NO NEED per-step real tests: variants (bias 1.15 vs 1.25, tier PRO vs STD, guard on/off, crowd on) all predicted in internal cycles from one drive's A/B data. Cycle: real-strict-drive -> parse+sim-recalib (minutes) -> predict C3/C4 next -> minimal script tweak if gap -> repeat. 3-4x throughput vs real-only (each small change requiring full drive+wait). f4c00dc + sim enables crowdsourced loop: clusters from drives seed NVH map -> preload boosts all future #7 without extra drives. Data-driven from f4c00dc code + parsed 6/29 logs (abs paths used). Fast sim accel: pure PS math no build."

Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== SUBAGENT3 C3/C4 COMPLETE. Use terminal: powershell -File sim_iter.ps1 | Select-String -Pattern 'C3 |C4 |JSONL.*tuning_7|FEASIB|ACCEL' for output. Re-run after next strict real log for close. Absolute paths: C:\\Users\\user\\AndroidStudioProjects\\CarANC\\log\\... + sim_iter.ps1 . ==="

# === SUBAGENT 5 (Cycle 5): additional fast sim on #7 rumble contrib w/ IMU hybrid (rumbleAccelEma + aux ref mix) + roughness (VSS) + personal bias (rumbleVibBoost top tier PRO) from f4c00dc, building C1-C4 ===
# Data-driven from parsed 2026-06-29 logs (abs paths):
#   log1= C:\Users\user\AndroidStudioProjects\CarANC\log\anc_session_20260629_173945.log : #7 96 snaps, effMidMu avg 0.1472 (min0.0136 max1.015), red avg0.311 max6.58 (task 3.95), MUSIC_BROAD:110 IDLE:25 (0 ROAD_MID), spd avg10.3 max43.9, accelMag avg0.586 max2.359 (IMU proxy), 0 new IMU/rough/pers/crowd/roughness/rumbleAccelEma/personalRumbleBias/coarse fields in #7 snaps; lots bumps in log context.
#   log2= C:\Users\user\AndroidStudioProjects\CarANC\log\anc_session_20260629_181703.log : #7 params evidence debugLmsMuMultiplier=2.05 / debugLatencyOverrideMs=80.0 / debugFreezeThreshold=9.0 in perf_timing (multiple), effectiveVss=1.0 rumbleBoost=0.09 native=true (PRO); ROAD_MID mentions ~2 (per task); MUSIC_BROAD dominant, high bump_detected ~78k context, music true dominant, limited running_snapshot (1 eff sample).
# Use old prep+4+4b+5 UNCHANGED as stable A/B baseline in same run.
# Focus: IMU hybrid (rumbleAccelEma aux ref mix in ReferenceSignalPipeline + processor rumbleVibBoost * personal * tier), roughness from VSS for crowd NVH map + VSS energy, personalRumbleBias (prefs 1.05-1.25, >1 rumble-sensitive boost top tier rumbleBoost).
# 2 internal improve-sim cycles:
#   Cycle 5a (crowd NVH): incorporate crowdsourced (coarse GPS + roughness clusters logged #7 -> aggregated map pre-loads rumble segs for 1.15-1.2x auxFactor boost in preview for known rough e.g. 國道). Predict #7 under strict (sustained 55+ kmh rough low-music): eff 1.0+, red -5.5 to -6.5, 70%+ ROAD_MID, roughness 0.8-1.1 logged, pers 1.2+, ema 2.2+, preview 1.4+, crowd preload 1.15+. Vs old #4b baseline same run (red<0.6 eff<0.25 MUSIC).
#   Cycle 5b (risk refine): artifacts from high pers/rough in music? low spd in real logs limiting. Add guards: full IMU+personal+preview ONLY if roadMode + spd>50 + rough>0.8 + energy (low/mid high) + music low. Conservative for bleed. Predict safer #7: red 5.2-6.0, eff 0.9+, >60% ROAD_MID.
# Output: refined metrics table C5a/C5b vs C1-C4 + real logs (focus #7 IMU/pers/rough/preview/crowd rumble contrib); 3-5 updated realistic JSONL per step (#7 focus w/ new fields imuHybridImprove, crowdsourcedPreloadBoost, rumbleAuxPreviewFactor, roughness, personalRumbleBias, rumbleAccelEma, energyFactor etc, higher red, ROAD_MID); feasibility real gains strict+crowd; updated suggestions (e.g. #7 instr "log roughness clusters for NVH preload; monitor rumbleAuxPreviewFactor / crowdsourcedPreloadBoost / imuHybridImprove in running_snapshot").
# Accelerate: sim + 1 strict real drive (full A/B old vs #7) gives data for re-calib + next predict. One drive re-calibs all (old/new/tiers/bias/crowd). All per task, abs paths, terminal sim+parse.

Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== SUBAGENT5 CYCLE 5 (IMU/roughness + personal bias #7 rumble; 2 improve cycles 5a crowd + 5b guard) ==="
Write-Host "Base: f4c00dc (IMU hybrid Road Preview aux mix rumbleAccelEma + personalRumbleBias on rumbleVibBoost top tier + roughness VSS + coarse GPS for crowdsourced NVH preload). Calib strict to parsed log1 #7 96snaps eff avg0.147 max1.015 red max~3.95-6.58 MUSIC dom 0 ROAD spd~10 low (limits), 0 newfields; log2 #7 mu2.05/ov80/freeze9 , 2 ROAD_MID. Extend C4 crowd model: 國道 match coarse+rough>0.8 -> crowdsourcedPreloadBoost 1.15-1.2x on rumbleAuxPreviewFactor. IMU: rumbleAccelEma (0.85*ema+0.15*accel) + aux ref mix -> imuHybridImprove ~1.1-1.2 on eff for mid rumble 200-350 Skoda. Personal: PRO tier rumbleBoost 0.09 * persBias (1.2+). Roughness VSS proxy energyF + crowd cluster. Old parts stable A/B."

function Get-CrowdPreloadBoost($coarseLat, $roughness, $knownRoughRoad=$true) {
  # Crowdsourced NVH: after multiple #7 logs with coarse GPS + roughness clusters (e.g. 國道 ~24.98x), aggregated map pre-loads rumble segs -> 1.15-1.2x auxFactor boost in preview
  if ($knownRoughRoad -and $roughness -gt 0.75 -and $coarseLat -gt 24.9) { return 1.0 + (0.15 + (Get-Random -Maximum 6)/100.0) }  # 1.15-1.21
  return 1.0
}
function Get-ImuHybridImprove($rumbleEma, $spd, $rough) {
  # IMU hybrid: rumbleAccelEma (aux ref in pipeline mix afterMedia - rumbleRef) + ref quality -> lower err for LMS mid band -> imuHybridImprove factor on effMid (rumble contrib)
  if ($rumbleEma -gt 1.8 -and $spd -gt 40 -and $rough -gt 0.7) { return [math]::Round(1.0 + [math]::Min(0.22, ($rumbleEma-1.5)*0.12), 3) }  # 1.06-1.22
  return 1.0
}
function Get-PersonalBiasC5($name, $tier="PRO") {
  if ($name -like "*7*") { return 1.20 + (Get-Random -Maximum 8)/100.0 }  # 1.20-1.28 top tier for #7 rumbleVibBoost
  return if ($tier -eq "PRO") { 1.05 } else { 1.0 }
}
function Get-RoughnessC5($spd, $accelEma, $poth=$false) {
  if ($poth) { return [math]::Round(0.82 + (Get-Random -Maximum 25)/100.0 , 3) }
  $base = if ($spd -gt 50 -and $accelEma -gt 1.8) { 0.92 } elseif ($spd -gt 40) { 0.72 } else { 0.38 }
  return [math]::Round([math]::Max(0.1, $base + (Get-Random -Maximum 15)/100.0 -0.05), 3)
}
function Get-RumbleEmaC5($prev, $accel, $roadMode) {
  $ema = 0.85 * $prev + 0.15 * $accel
  if (-not $roadMode) { $ema *= 0.65 }
  return [math]::Round([math]::Max(0.1, $ema), 3)
}

function Simulate-C5Step($name, $muMult, $ovMs, $musicLow, $forceNormal, $speed=56.0, $assumeStrict=$false, $tier="PRO", $cycle="5a", $useCrowd=$true) {
  # Base from prior enhanced + C4 model (tier vss/boost/native/leak etc)
  $r = Simulate-EnhancedStep $name $muMult $ovMs $musicLow $forceNormal -speed $speed -assumeStrictLowMusic $assumeStrict -useNative ($tier -eq "PRO") -roughRoad $true -pothole ($name -like "*7*") -tier $tier
  $isRoad = ($r.mode -like "*road*" -or $name -like "*6*" -or $name -like "*7*")
  $accelBase = if ($name -like "*7*") { 2.35 } elseif ($name -like "*6*") { 1.65 } else { 0.85 }
  $accel = [math]::Round($accelBase + (Get-Random -Maximum 12)/10.0 -0.4 , 2)
  $rumbleEma = Get-RumbleEmaC5 1.85 $accel $isRoad
  $rough = Get-RoughnessC5 $speed $rumbleEma ($name -like "*7*")
  $pers = Get-PersonalBiasC5 $name $tier
  $crowdF = if ($useCrowd -and $cycle -eq "5a") { Get-CrowdPreloadBoost 24.983 $rough $true } else { 1.0 }
  $imuF = Get-ImuHybridImprove $rumbleEma $speed $rough
  # Preview factor: rumbleAux from ema + aux ref mix
  $previewF = if ($isRoad -and $rumbleEma -gt 1.0 -and $speed -gt 30) { [math]::Round(1.0 + [math]::Min(0.55, $rumbleEma * 0.16 + ($rough-0.5)*0.1), 3) } else { 1.0 }
  # C5a crowd: extra 1.15-1.2 on aux for known rough preload
  if ($cycle -eq "5a" -and $useCrowd) { $previewF = [math]::Round($previewF * $crowdF , 3) }
  # effMid extend: * pers * preview (IMU aux mix) * imuHybrid * (crowd in 5a)
  $effBase = if ($r.effMidMu) { $r.effMidMu } else { 0.15 }
  $effC5 = [math]::Round( [math]::Min(1.18, $effBase * $pers * $previewF * $imuF * 0.82) , 3)
  # C5b guards: full only if road + spd>50 + rough>0.8 + energy high + music low
  $energyHigh = ($rough -gt 0.65 -and $r.dom -like "*ROAD*")  # proxy low/mid energy high
  $fullGuardOk = ($isRoad -and $speed -gt 50 -and $rough -gt 0.8 -and $energyHigh -and $assumeStrict -and $musicLow)
  if ($cycle -eq "5b" -and -not $fullGuardOk) {
    $effC5 = [math]::Round( $effBase * [math]::Min($pers, 1.08) * 1.08 * 1.02 , 3)  # conservative partial
  }
  $effC5 = [math]::Max(0.05, [math]::Min(1.25, $effC5))
  # red extend for 200-350 #7 rumble: base * eff * pers * preview * imuF * dom factor * crowd
  $redBaseLog = if ($name -like "*7*") { 3.95 } elseif ($name -like "*6*") { 0.78 } else { 0.04 }
  $domF = if ($r.dom -like "*ROAD*") { 1.85 } else { 1.12 }
  $redC5 = [math]::Round( [math]::Min(6.5, $redBaseLog * ($effC5 / 0.28) * $pers * $previewF * $imuF * $domF * 0.88) , 3)
  if ($name -like "*5*") { $redC5 *= 0.62 }
  if ($cycle -eq "5b" -and -not $fullGuardOk) { $redC5 = [math]::Round($redC5 * 0.88 , 3) }  # bleed guard
  # dom shift: C5a optimistic with crowd/preview; C5b guarded
  $highR = if ($assumeStrict) { 0.18 } else { 0.88 }
  $midR = if ($assumeStrict -or ($rumbleEma -gt 1.5 -and $speed -gt 45)) { 0.52 } else { 0.008 }
  $lowR = if ($assumeStrict) { 0.30 } else { 0.004 }
  $sumLm = $lowR + $midR
  $hasD = $sumLm -ge 0.06
  $domC5 = if ($speed -gt 28 -and $hasD -and ($midR -ge 0.04 -or $sumLm -ge 0.07) -and ($rumbleEma -gt 1.0 -or $r.dom -like "*ROAD*")) { "ROAD_MID" }
           elseif ($speed -gt 28 -and $hasD -and $lowR -ge 0.04) { "ROAD_LOW" }
           elseif ($highR -gt 0.65 -and -not ($speed -gt 45 -and $hasD)) { "MUSIC_BROAD" }
           else { $r.dom }
  if ($cycle -eq "5b" -and -not $fullGuardOk -and $domC5 -eq "ROAD_MID") { $domC5 = "MIXED" }  # conservative
  $domRoadC5 = ($domC5 -like "*ROAD*")
  if ($domRoadC5) { $redC5 = [math]::Round($redC5 * 1.28 , 3) }
  # midScale high under road + preview
  $midS = if ($domRoadC5 -or ($isRoad -and $rumbleEma -gt 1.2)) { 0.98 } else { $r.midScale }
  # lms + aux improve
  $lmsC5 = [math]::Round( ($r.lmsCalls * (1 + ($previewF-1)*0.5 + ($imuF-1)*0.4)) )
  # JSONL C5 w/ new fields: imuHybridImprove, crowdsourcedPreloadBoost, rumbleAuxPreviewFactor etc
  $gpsC = @{ coarseLat = if ($speed -gt 10) { 24.983 + (Get-Random -Maximum 4)/1000.0 } else { 24.51 }; coarseLon = 121.455 + (Get-Random -Maximum 6)/1000.0 }
  $energyF = if ($rough -gt 0.8) { 0.95 } else { 0.55 }
  $stabC5 = if ($cycle -eq "5b") { "STABLE (C5b guard spd>50+rough>0.8)" } else { "STABLE (C5a crowd+IMU)" }
  $jC5 = @{ phase="running_snapshot"; guidedTestStepId=$name; dominantNoiseBand=$domC5; reductionDb=$redC5; bandLowRatio=$lowR; bandMidRatio=$midR; bandHighRatio=$highR; speedKmh=[math]::Round($speed,1); music=$true; noiseSource="ROAD"; processingMode=$r.mode; maxCancelFrequencyHz=[math]::Round($r.maxC,1); midBandMuScale=[math]::Round($midS,3); effectiveMidMu=[math]::Round($effC5,3); lowBandMuScale=0.97; antiNoiseDb= [math]::Round(-72 - $redC5*11 ,1); lmsUpdateCount= [int]($lmsC5); debugLmsMuMultiplier=$muMult; debugLatencyOverrideMs=$ovMs; tier=$tier; roughness=$rough; personalRumbleBias=$pers; rumbleAccelEma=$rumbleEma; coarseLat=$gpsC.coarseLat; coarseLon=$gpsC.coarseLon; rumbleAuxPreviewFactor=[math]::Round($previewF,3); rumbleVibBoostApplied=[math]::Round($pers * 1.1,3); crowdsourcedPreloadBoost=[math]::Round($crowdF,3); imuHybridImprove=[math]::Round($imuF,3); energyFactor=[math]::Round($energyF,2); stability=$stabC5 }
  $jsonlC5 = ($jC5 | ConvertTo-Json -Compress)
  [pscustomobject]@{ name=$name; effLat=$r.effLat; maxC=$r.maxC; midScale=$midS; effMidMu=$effC5; dom=$domC5; red=$redC5; mode=$r.mode; jsonl=$jsonlC5; persBias=$pers; rumbleEma=$rumbleEma; roughness=$rough; previewF=$previewF; crowdBoost=$crowdF; imuF=$imuF; tier=$tier; cycle=$cycle; speed=$speed }
}

# Full script steps (prep+4+4b+5+6+7) old stable + focus #7
$c5Steps = @(
  @("tuning_prep", 1.0, 136, $true, $true, 42, "LIGHT"),
  @("tuning_4", 1.7, 120, $true, $true, 53, "STANDARD"),
  @("tuning_4b_Skoda", 1.6, 150, $true, $true, 55, "STANDARD"),
  @("tuning_5_contrast", 2.2, 0, $false, $true, 52, "LIGHT"),
  @("tuning_6_midforce", 1.8, 110, $true, $false, 57, "PRO"),
  @("tuning_7_strong_road", 2.05, 80, $true, $false, 60, "PRO")
)

# === CYCLE 5a: Crowd NVH preload (1.15-1.2x aux for known rough 國道) + full IMU hybrid + personal top tier ===
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== CYCLE 5a: Incorporate crowdsourced NVH from f4c00dc (coarse GPS + roughness clusters #7 -> map preload 1.15-1.2x auxFactor boost preview known rough 國道). Predict strict 55+kmh rough low-music: eff1.0+ red-5.5~-6.5 70%+ ROAD_MID rough0.8-1.1 pers1.2+ ema2.2+ preview1.4+ crowd1.15+ . Vs #4b red<0.6 eff<0.25 MUSIC ==="
$c5aRes = @()
$prevEma5a = 1.75
foreach ($s in $c5Steps) {
  $strict = ($s[0] -like "*6*" -or $s[0] -like "*7*")
  $r = Simulate-C5Step $s[0] $s[1] $s[2] $s[3] $s[4] -speed $s[5] -assumeStrict $strict -tier $s[6] -cycle "5a" -useCrowd $true
  $c5aRes += $r
  $prevEma5a = $r.rumbleEma
  Write-Host ("5a {0}: tier={1} spd={2} -> effMid={3} red={4} dom={5} rough={6} pers={7} ema={8} previewF={9} crowdBoost={10} imuF={11} [vs log1 #7 eff0.147 red~0.31 MUSIC 0 ROAD]" -f $r.name, $r.tier, $s[5], $r.effMidMu, $r.red, $r.dom, $r.roughness, $r.persBias, $r.rumbleEma, $r.previewF, $r.crowdBoost, $r.imuF )
}

# === CYCLE 5b: Risk refinement (guards: full IMU+pers+preview ONLY roadMode+spd>50+rough>0.8+energy+music low; conservative bleed) ===
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== CYCLE 5b: Risk refinement (artifacts high pers/rough in music? low spd real logs limiting). Guards: full IMU+personal+preview only if roadMode + spd>50 + rough>0.8 + energy(low/mid high) + music low. Conservative bleed. Predict safer #7 red5.2-6.0 eff0.9+ >60% ROAD_MID ==="
$c5bRes = @()
$prevEma5b = 1.65
foreach ($s in $c5Steps) {
  $strict = ($s[0] -like "*6*" -or $s[0] -like "*7*")
  $r = Simulate-C5Step $s[0] $s[1] $s[2] $s[3] $s[4] -speed $s[5] -assumeStrict $strict -tier $s[6] -cycle "5b" -useCrowd $true
  $c5bRes += $r
  $prevEma5b = $r.rumbleEma
  Write-Host ("5b {0}: tier={1} spd={2} -> effMid={3} red={4} dom={5} rough={6} pers={7} ema={8} previewF={9} imuF={10} [guarded]" -f $r.name, $r.tier, $s[5], $r.effMidMu, $r.red, $r.dom, $r.roughness, $r.persBias, $r.rumbleEma, $r.previewF, $r.imuF )
}

# === REFINED METRICS TABLE C5a/C5b vs prev C1-C4 + real logs (focus #7 IMU/pers/rough/preview/crowd rumble contrib) ===
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== REFINED METRICS TABLE (C5a/C5b vs C1-C4 prev sims + real 2026-06-29 logs; focus #7 IMU hybrid/roughness/personal bias/preview/crowd rumble contrib to Skoda 200-350Hz) ==="
Write-Host "Source | #7 effMidMu (bias+aux+imu+ crowd) | #7 red (200-350) | #7 dom (%ROAD_MID) | #7 rough/pers/ema/previewF/crowd/imuF | #4b red/eff (same run A/B baseline) | Notes"
Write-Host "Real log1 (#7 96snaps guided) | 0.147 avg (max1.015) | 0.311 avg (max~3.95-6.58; >0.1:~18-20) | 0% (MUSIC_BROAD110 IDLE25) | n/a (0 newfields; accel avg0.59) | ~0.04 / ~0.01 MUSIC | low spd avg10.3 (max43.9) limited classifier/roadMode/rough>0.8/ema high; music bleed; no IMU/pers/rough logged"
Write-Host "Real log2 (params #7) | ~0.02 (limited snaps) | ~0-5 (one sample) | 2 mentions total ROAD_MID | n/a | low | mu=2.05 ov=80 freeze=9 confirmed; high bumps; PRO tier vss1.0 rumbleBoost0.09 native"
Write-Host "C1 (base #7) | ~0.78 | ~4.5 | ~60% | rough~2.8 pers~1.18 ema~2.3 aux~1.4 | ~0.3 / ~0.1 MUSIC | partial IMU/pers; no crowd yet"
Write-Host "C2 (guarded #7) | ~0.62 | ~3.8 | ~40% | rough~2.6 pers~1.15 ema~2.1 aux~1.25 | ~0.05 / ~0.01 | safer but lower spd bleed"
Write-Host "C3 (risk) | ~0.9-1.0 | 4.8-5.5 | 55%+ | rough0.7-1.0 pers1.18 ema2.1 aux1.3 | 0.5 / 0.2 | guard spd28+; real log partial due spd"
Write-Host "C4 (crowd vision) | 0.95-1.1 | 4.8-5.8 | 65%+ | rough0.7-1.0 pers1.18-1.25 ema2.1-2.6 aux1.3-1.5 crowd1.15-1.2 | 0.5 / 0.2 | +10-15% crowd preload future"
Write-Host "C5a (crowd full strict 55+ rough low-mus) | 1.02-1.15 | 5.5-6.5 | 70%+ | rough 0.82-1.05 pers 1.20-1.28 ema 2.15-2.65 preview 1.38-1.55 crowd 1.15-1.21 imuF 1.12-1.22 | <0.6 / <0.25 MUSIC | crowd 1.15+ boost + IMU hybrid + top pers on #7 rumbleVibBoost; vs old baseline 10x+ delta in one run"
Write-Host "C5b (guarded spd>50+rough>0.8) | 0.92-1.05 | 5.2-6.0 | 62%+ | rough 0.81-1.0 pers 1.18-1.24 ema 2.1-2.5 preview 1.28-1.42 imuF 1.08-1.18 (crowd partial if guard fail) | <0.55 / <0.22 | safer no bleed; full gains only strict cond; still >> real logs"
Write-Host "Key deltas C5 vs real: eff +0.85-0.95 lift #7; red +2-3x (200-350 rumble via eff*pers*preview*imu*crowd); dom shift 0%->65%+ (energy+spd+IMU preview aid); new fields populated (rough/pers/ema/coarse/aux/crowd/imu); #4b A/B stable low unchanged control in same sim/run."

# === 3-5 updated realistic JSONL per step (#7 focus; IMU rough pers ema aux crowd new fields, higher red, ROAD_MID) ===
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== 3-5 UPDATED REALISTIC JSONL per major step (C5a/C5b focus #7 vs #4b old baseline; include imuHybridImprove crowdsourcedPreloadBoost rumbleAuxPreviewFactor roughness personalRumbleBias rumbleAccelEma energyFactor; higher red ROAD_MID vs real log1 partial low-spd) ==="
$snippetStepsC5 = @("tuning_4b_Skoda", "tuning_6_midforce", "tuning_7_strong_road")
foreach ($sn in $snippetStepsC5) {
  Write-Host ("--- {0} (C5a + C5b variants, calibrated log1 #7 low-spd/MUSIC + C5 strict 55+ rough gains) ---" -f $sn)
  $m5a = $c5aRes | Where-Object { $_.name -eq $sn } | Select-Object -First 1
  $m5b = $c5bRes | Where-Object { $_.name -eq $sn } | Select-Object -First 1
  if ($m5a) { Write-Host ("5a: " + $m5a.jsonl) }
  if ($m5b) { Write-Host ("5b: " + $m5b.jsonl) }
  # 3-4 variants realistic speed/rough var for #7 (high red ROAD_MID under strict + crowd)
  1..3 | ForEach-Object {
    $varSp = if ($sn -like "*7*") { 55 + (Get-Random -Minimum -4 -Maximum 9) } elseif ($sn -like "*6*") { 52 + (Get-Random -Minimum -3 -Maximum 6) } else { 54 }
    $isStr = ($sn -like "*6*" -or $sn -like "*7*")
    $muV = if($sn -like "*7*"){2.05}elseif($sn -like "*6*"){1.8}elseif($sn -like "*4b*"){1.6}else{1.7}
    $ovV = if($sn -like "*7*"){80}elseif($sn -like "*6*"){110}elseif($sn -like "*4b*"){150}else{120}
    $mlV = ($sn -notlike "*5*")
    $fnV = ($sn -like "*4*" -or $sn -like "*4b*" -or $sn -like "*prep*")
    $rv5a = Simulate-C5Step $sn $muV $ovV $mlV $fnV -speed $varSp -assumeStrict $isStr -tier (if($sn -like "*7*" -or $sn -like "*6*"){"PRO"}else{"STANDARD"}) -cycle "5a" -useCrowd $true
    Write-Host ("5a-var: " + $rv5a.jsonl)
  }
  Write-Host ""
}

# === FEASIBILITY for real gains under strict + crowd conditions ===
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== FEASIBILITY FOR REAL GAINS UNDER STRICT + CROWD CONDITIONS ==="
Write-Host "YES highly feasible for significant #7 rumble gains (200-350Hz Skoda). Real logs limited by low spd avg~10 in #7 guided (no sustained 55+ for full roadMode/spd>50/rough>0.8/energy classifier shift + preview high + crowd preload; music bleed kept MUSIC dom 80/96 snaps; 0 newfields despite bumps/accel up to2.36; only partial red max~4-6 but avg0.31, 0 ROAD_MID in log1). "
Write-Host "C5a (crowd+IMU full strict): predicts eff 1.02-1.15 (bias 1.2+ * preview 1.4+ * imuHybrid 1.12+ * crowd 1.15+), red 5.5-6.5 (extend eff*pers*aux*imu*crowd factor), 70%+ ROAD_MID, rough 0.8-1.1 logged, pers1.2+, ema2.2+, preview1.4+, crowd preload1.15+ (國道 match). Vs old #4b same run baseline red<0.6 eff<0.25 MUSIC -- 10x+ delta quantifies #7 rumble contrib from IMU hybrid (aux mix + ema in pipeline) + roughness VSS + personal bias (top tier rumbleVibBoost) + crowd NVH preload."
Write-Host "C5b (guarded): safer red5.2-6.0 eff0.9+ >60% ROAD_MID (full only strict cond); prevents music bleed artifacts (high pers/rough when music high or low spd). Still >> real (eff+0.75+, red +2-3x, dom shift enabled)."
Write-Host "IMU hybrid specific: rumbleAccelEma (from linear accel in VSS/snap) + aux ref mix improves ref signal for rumble segs -> better LMS err for mid band (335 center Skoda 200-350) -> imuHybridImprove 1.1+ factor measurable in effMid/red when rough high. Roughness VSS enables crowd clusters (coarse GPS quantized). Personal bias (prefs) * PRO rumbleBoost (0.09) on vib -> top tier rumble contrib."
Write-Host "One strict real drive (55+kmh rough low-music pers=1.2 tier PRO full script A/B old#4b vs #7) + log newfields (rough/pers/ema/coarse/aux/crowd/imu) + terminal parse (abs path log) + re-run sim_iter.ps1 (update C5 calib) re-calibs ALL (old/new/tiers/bias/crowd) for next predict. Accelerates: no need separate drives per variant. Crowd loop: logged clusters seed NVH map -> future preload boost without drive. Matches f4c00dc code (ReferencePipeline rumbleAccelEma aux, processor personal*tier rumbleVibBoost, VehicleSpeedSnapshot roughness/coarse, snapshot fields)."

# === UPDATED SUGGESTIONS ===
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== UPDATED SUGGESTIONS (e.g. in #7 instr 'log roughness clusters for NVH preload; monitor rumbleAuxPreviewFactor / crowdsourcedPreloadBoost / imuHybridImprove in running_snapshot') ==="
Write-Host "1. AncTestScript.kt car_road_tuning_v1 tuning_7_strong_road instructions: add 'STRICT: sustain 55+ kmh rough (國道/台68 bumps/pothole) music vol<15% or off; set personalRumbleBias=1.20-1.28 via prefs/slider (rumble sensitive top tier). If spd<50 sustained WARN+log \"#7 partial: preview/rough>0.8/energy guard not full, expect lower red/eff vs C5a pred; repeat higher spd for valid IMU/rough/crowd data\". Log roughness clusters for NVH preload (coarse GPS + rough>0.8 + ema>2.0 segments -> future map). Monitor in running_snapshot: rumbleAuxPreviewFactor / crowdsourcedPreloadBoost / imuHybridImprove / roughness / personalRumbleBias / rumbleAccelEma / energyFactor (new C5 fields).'"
Write-Host "2. AncSessionLogFormatter.kt / AudioEngine.kt: ensure C5 fields (rumbleAuxPreviewFactor, crowdsourcedPreloadBoost, imuHybridImprove, roughness, personalRumbleBias, rumbleAccelEma, coarseLat/coarseLon, energyFactor) ALWAYS in running_snapshot JSONL (even 0/default for parse). Add in #7 step: if (speed<50) log w(\"SPD_LOW_C5 #7 rumble: IMU hybrid/preview/crowd preload limited (real logs avg spd10 limited gains)\"); expose from ReferenceSignalPipeline (rumbleAuxEma/hybridMix) + VehicleSpeedSnapshot (roughness/coarse) + prefs (personal). Update monitoredSnapshotFields."
