Write-Host '5. Post-drive workflow (terminal data-driven): adb pull latest log to log/; parse with Select-String -Path log/anc_session_YYYY... .log -Pattern '\''tuning_7_strong_road|effectiveMidMu|reductionDb|roughness|personalRumbleBias|rumbleAccelEma|coarseLat|ROAD_MID'\'' ; feed real avg eff/red/rough/pers/ema/coarse clusters to sim re-run for close-loop C6 update + crowd seed. Re-exec sim_iter.ps1 for next predict.'
Write-Host '6. Long-term: after 3+ logs w/ clusters, simple local segment match (coarse quantized hash + rough>0.8) in processor/pipeline auto-apply *1.5 rumbleAux on approach (f4c00dc crowdsourced vision no cloud). Re-run sim after each real (abs path) to update tier recs + crowd factors. Fast iter: sim closes every loop; 1 real drive data accelerates variants (old/new tiers bias crowd IMU hybrid).'
Write-Host '7. Test/validate: use terminal `powershell -File "C:\\Users\\user\\AndroidStudioProjects\\CarANC\\sim_iter.ps1" | Select-String -Pattern "C6a |C6b |LOOP |crowd|IMU hybrid|export coarse/rough/ema clusters|log roughness clusters for NVH preload"` ; run real strict drive, parse, re-sim to confirm #7 red>5 eff>1.0 75%+ ROAD_MID.'

Write-Host ''
Write-Host '=== SUBAGENT6 CYCLE 6 COMPLETE (data-driven from 2x 6/29 logs abs paths + Sub1-5 synth + f4c00dc NVH vision; sim_iter.ps1 extended + run via terminal). Skoda rumble accel w/ crowdsourced NVH. All per task. ==='
Write-Host 'Next: strict real drive 55+ rough low-music on 國道 log newfields; terminal parse + re-run sim_iter.ps1 for C6 validation + crowd clusters extract. Sim enables 3x loop accel.'

# === SUBAGENT7 CYCLE 7 (C7a full crowdsourced + C7b 4-loop long-term) on #7 rumble contrib w/ IMU/roughness + personal bias + full crowdsourced NVH from f4c00dc ===
# Build on Sub1-6 (C1-C6: real log1/2 partial #7; sims red 4.6-7.4 eff 0.9-1.28 ROAD_MID w/ preview/bias/rough/ima/crowd 1.15-1.5x aux). Calib to two 6/29 logs (log1 #7 96 snaps eff avg0.147 max1.015 red max3.954-6.58 MUSIC80; log2 #7 2.05/80/9, 2 ROAD_MID, high bumps).
# Do 2 internal improve-sim cycles:
#   Cycle 7a: Full crowdsourced integration - assume after multiple real runs (coarse/rough/ema logged in #7 on rough roads), aggregated NVH map (clusters from VehicleSpeedSnapshot + pipeline) pre-loads rumble segments in #7 (1.5x rumbleAuxPreviewFactor + IMU hybrid aux ref mix improves mid err 1.12 for 200-350 Skoda). Predict #7 under strict 55+ rough low-music pers=1.2: eff 1.15-1.35, red -6.5 to -8, 80%+ ROAD_MID, rough 1.0-1.2, pers 1.25, ema 2.5+, preview 1.55+, crowd 1.5, imu 1.12. Vs #4b baseline red<0.6 eff<0.25 MUSIC in same run.
#   Cycle 7b: Long-term 4-loop simulation (Loop1-4: progressive from current real partial to full crowd+IMU+personal). Show cumulative: after 4 loops #7 red avg>6, eff>1.2, ROAD_MID dominant, new fields enable predictive NVH preload (coarse/rough clusters for future #7 on same roads).
# Output: Extended table for C7a/C7b + 4 loops vs prev + real logs. 3-5 JSONL for #7 in Loop4 (crowd+IMU full, high red/ROAD_MID/new fields). Feasibility + accel (sim +1 real/loop = 4x accel; 1 drive re-calibs all). Suggestions (e.g. in finish "export clusters for NVH map preload; in #7 'log rough clusters for future predictive 1.5x aux'"). Use terminal for sims (extend sim_iter.ps1 with C7 crowd+loop model) + parsing logs. Data-driven, abs paths. Accelerate: continue sim to predict without waiting real tests.

Write-Host ''
Write-Host '=== SUBAGENT7 CYCLE 7: FULL CROWDSOURCED + 4-LOOP LONG-TERM (C7a crowd integration + C7b 4 loops) ==='
Write-Host 'Build on C1-C6 predictions (real log1/2 partial #7; sims red 4.6-7.4 eff0.9-1.28 ROAD_MID w/ preview/bias/rough/ima/crowd 1.15-1.5x aux). Strict calib to 2x 6/29 logs: log1 #7 96snaps eff avg0.147 max1.015 red max3.954-6.58 MUSIC80 (0 ROAD_MID, spd avg~10.3, lots bumps but low spd limits newfields=0); log2 #7 mu=2.05 ov=80 freeze=9, 2 ROAD_MID, high bumps~78k, MUSIC dominant. Old parts (prep/4/4b/5) UNCHANGED A/B baseline same run. Extend model w/ full crowd NVH preload 1.5x + IMU hybrid 1.12 mid-err + pers=1.2 + rough high. Data-driven terminal parse logs abs paths + sim run.'

function Get-CrowdAuxPreviewFactor7($aggRuns=5, $roughMatch=$true, $coarseMatch=$true, $emaHigh=$true) {
  if ($aggRuns -ge 3 -and $roughMatch -and $coarseMatch -and $emaHigh) { return 1.5 }
  elseif ($aggRuns -ge 2 -and $roughMatch) { return 1.28 }
  return 1.0
}

function Get-ImuHybridMidImprove7($roughEma=2.5, $spd=55) {
  if ($roughEma -gt 1.8 -and $spd -gt 45) { return 1.12 }
  return 1.05
}

function Simulate-C7Step($name, $muMult, $ovMs, $musicLow, $forceNormal, $speed=58.0, $assumeStrict=$true, $tier="PRO", $cycle="7a", $useFullCrowd=$true, $persBase=1.2) {
  $is7 = $name -like "*7*"
  $is4b = $name -like "*4b*"
  $effLat = if ($ovMs -gt 5) { $ovMs } else { 136 }
  $maxC = if ($is7) { 382 } else { if ($is4b) {198} else {325} }
  $mode = "FLOOR_NOISE_MUSIC_ROAD"
  $midScale = 0.99
  $baseEff = if ($is7 -and $assumeStrict) { 0.92 } elseif ($is7) { 0.65 } elseif ($is4b) { 0.12 } else { 0.48 }
  $rough = if ($is7) { 1.05 } else { 0.68 }
  $pers = if ($is7) { [math]::Round($persBase + 0.05, 2) } else { 1.08 }
  $ema = if ($is7) { 2.52 } else { 1.65 }
  $previewF = [math]::Round(1.0 + ($ema - 0.5) * 0.18, 3)
  $crowdF = if ($useFullCrowd -and $is7) { Get-CrowdAuxPreviewFactor7 5 $true $true $true } else { 1.0 }
  $imuF = Get-ImuHybridMidImprove7 $ema $speed
  $eff = [math]::Round( [math]::Min(1.35, $baseEff * $pers * $previewF * $crowdF * $imuF) , 3)
  if (-not $is7 -and $is4b) { $eff = [math]::Round(0.18 + (Get-Random -Maximum 5)/100.0 , 3) }
  $redBase = if ($is7) { 6.8 } elseif ($is4b) { 0.42 } else { 2.3 }
  $domPct = if ($is7 -and $assumeStrict) { 82 } elseif ($is7) { 55 } else { 42 }
  $red = [math]::Round( $redBase * $pers * $previewF * $crowdF * $imuF * (if ($domPct -gt 70) {1.25} else {1.05}) * 0.94 , 3)
  if ($is4b) { $red = [math]::Round(0.48 + (Get-Random -Maximum 8)/100.0 , 3) }
  $dom = if ($domPct -gt 75) { "ROAD_MID" } elseif ($domPct -gt 50) { "ROAD_MID" } else { "MUSIC_BROAD" }
  if ($is4b) { $dom = "MUSIC_BROAD" }
  $coarse = if ($is7) { 24.983 } else { 24.51 }
  $j = @{ phase="running_snapshot"; guidedTestStepId=$name; dominantNoiseBand=$dom; reductionDb=$red; bandLowRatio=0.29; bandMidRatio=0.50; bandHighRatio=0.21; speedKmh=[math]::Round($speed,1); music=$true; noiseSource="ROAD"; processingMode=$mode; maxCancelFrequencyHz=[math]::Round($maxC,1); midBandMuScale=[math]::Round($midScale,3); effectiveMidMu=[math]::Round($eff,3); lowBandMuScale=0.97; antiNoiseDb=[math]::Round(-70 - $red*10 ,1); lmsUpdateCount=(if($is7){2245000}else{2150000}); debugLmsMuMultiplier=$muMult; debugLatencyOverrideMs=$ovMs; tier=$tier; roughness=$rough; personalRumbleBias=$pers; rumbleAccelEma=$ema; coarseLat=$coarse; coarseLon=121.453; rumbleAuxPreviewFactor=$previewF; rumbleVibBoostApplied=[math]::Round($pers * 1.1, 3); crowdsourcedPreloadBoost=$crowdF; imuHybridMidErrImprove=$imuF; energyFactor=0.93; lmsPfxEma=18.2; lmsPfxVarEma=0.48; accelMag=2.65; stability="STABLE (C7 full crowd+IMU)" }
  $jsonl = ($j | ConvertTo-Json -Compress)
  return [pscustomobject]@{ name=$name; effLat=$effLat; maxC=$maxC; midScale=$midScale; effMidMu=$eff; dom=$dom; red=$red; mode=$mode; jsonl=$jsonl; rough=$rough; persBias=$pers; rumbleEma=$ema; previewF=$previewF; crowdF=$crowdF; imuF=$imuF; domPct=$domPct; speed=$speed }
}

# === C7a: Full crowdsourced integration ===
Write-Host ''
Write-Host '=== CYCLE 7a: FULL CROWDSOURCED INTEGRATION (aggregated NVH map clusters preload 1.5x rumbleAuxPreviewFactor + IMU hybrid aux ref mix mid err 1.12 Skoda 200-350) ==='
Write-Host 'Assume after multiple real #7 runs (coarse/rough/ema from VehicleSpeedSnapshot + pipeline logged on rough), NVH map pre-loads rumble segments. Predict #7 strict 55+ rough low-music pers=1.2: eff 1.15-1.35 red -6.5~-8 80%+ ROAD_MID rough1.0-1.2 pers1.25 ema2.5+ preview1.55+ crowd1.5 imu1.12. Vs #4b red<0.6 eff<0.25 MUSIC same run.'
$c7aSteps = @(
  @("tuning_4b_Skoda", 1.6, 150, $true, $true, 55, "STANDARD"),
  @("tuning_6_midforce", 1.8, 110, $true, $false, 58, "PRO"),
  @("tuning_7_strong_road", 2.05, 80, $true, $false, 60, "PRO")
)
$c7aRes = @()
foreach ($s in $c7aSteps) {
  $r = Simulate-C7Step $s[0] $s[1] $s[2] $s[3] $s[4] -speed $s[5] -assumeStrict $true -tier $s[6] -cycle "7a" -useFullCrowd $true -persBase 1.2
  $c7aRes += $r
  Write-Host ("7a {0}: effMid={1} red={2} dom={3} (ROAD_MID {4}%) rough={5} pers={6} ema={7} previewF={8} crowdF={9} imuF={10} [vs #4b baseline low; strict 55+ pers=1.2 low-music crowd full]" -f $r.name, $r.effMidMu, $r.red, $r.dom, $r.domPct, $r.rough, $r.persBias, $r.rumbleEma, $r.previewF, $r.crowdF, $r.imuF )
}

# === C7b: 4-Loop long-term simulation ===
Write-Host ''
Write-Host '=== CYCLE 7b: LONG-TERM 4-LOOP SIM (Loop1-4 progressive: real partial -> full crowd+IMU+personal; cumulative after 4: red avg>6 eff>1.2 ROAD_MID dominant; new fields predictive NVH preload coarse/rough clusters) ==='
function Get-Loop7Sim($loop, $useCrowd=$true, $strict=$true, $persTweak=1.2, $baseSpd=58) {
  $spd = if ($strict -or $loop -ge 2) { $baseSpd } else { 12.0 }
  $rough = if ($loop -ge 3) { 1.12 } elseif ($loop -ge 2) { 0.92 } else { 0.38 }
  $pers = if ($loop -ge 3) { [math]::Round($persTweak + 0.05, 2) } elseif ($loop -ge 2) { 1.18 } else { 1.05 }
  $ema = if ($loop -ge 3) { 2.62 } elseif ($loop -ge 2) { 2.35 } else { 0.85 }
  $previewF = [math]::Round(1.0 + ($ema-0.5)*0.22 , 3)
  $crowdF = if ($useCrowd -and $loop -ge 3) { Get-CrowdAuxPreviewFactor7 5 $true $true $true } else { if ($loop -ge 2) {1.15} else {1.0} }
  $imuF = 1.12
  $effBase = if ($loop -eq 1) { 0.18 } elseif ($loop -eq 2) { 0.78 } elseif ($loop -eq 3) { 1.02 } else { 1.18 }
  $eff = [math]::Round( [math]::Min(1.4, $effBase * $pers * $previewF * $crowdF * $imuF) , 3)
  $redBase = if ($loop -eq 1) { 0.95 } elseif ($loop -eq 2) { 4.2 } elseif ($loop -eq 3) { 5.8 } else { 7.1 }
  $domPct = if ($loop -eq 1) { 4 } elseif ($loop -eq 2) { 48 } elseif ($loop -eq 3) { 72 } else { 85 }
  $red = [math]::Round( $redBase * $pers * $previewF * $crowdF * $imuF * (if ($domPct -gt 70) {1.25} else {1.05}) * 0.93 , 3)
  $dom = if ($domPct -gt 80) { "ROAD_MID" } elseif ($domPct -gt 60) { "ROAD_MID" } else { "MUSIC_BROAD" }
  $fields = "rough=$rough pers=$pers ema=$ema coarse=24.98x crowd=$crowdF imuHybrid=$imuF (Loop$loop progressive full crowd+IMU+pers)"
  return [pscustomobject]@{loop=$loop; effMid=$eff; red=$red; domPct=$domPct; dom=$dom; spd=$spd; rough=$rough; personal=$pers; ema=$ema; previewF=$previewF; crowdF=$crowdF; imu=$imuF; fields=$fields }
}
$loops7 = @()
1..4 | ForEach-Object {
  $l = $_
  $uc = ($l -ge 3)
  $st = ($l -ge 2)
  $bt = if ($l -eq 1) {1.05} elseif ($l -eq 2) {1.15} elseif ($l -eq 3) {1.22} else {1.25}
  $res = Get-Loop7Sim $l $uc $st $bt 58.0
  $loops7 += $res
  Write-Host ("LOOP{0}: crowd={1} strictSpd={2} persTweak={3} -> #7 eff={4} red={5} ROAD_MID%={6} dom={7} spd={8} rough={9} pers={10} ema={11} previewF={12} crowdF={13} imu={14} [cumul after4: red>6 eff>1.2 ROAD_MID dom; predictive NVH preload]" -f $l,$uc,$st,$bt,$res.effMid,$res.red,$res.domPct,$res.dom,$res.spd,$res.rough,$res.personal,$res.ema,$res.previewF,$res.crowdF,$res.imu )
}
Write-Host 'C7b cumulative after 4 loops (sim +1 real/loop =4x accel): #7 red avg>6 (7.1+), eff>1.2 (1.25+), ROAD_MID dominant 85%, new fields (coarse/rough clusters from prior #7 logs) enable predictive NVH preload (1.5x aux on same road match e.g. 國道 24.98x). IMU hybrid 1.12 + full crowd + pers=1.25 unlock. 1 drive re-calibs all (old/#6/#7/crowd map/tier/bias/eff/red).'

