Write-Host 'Real log2 #7 | ~0.44 | avg0.13 (2 ROAD_MID total) | 2 total | n/a (high bumps) | low | mu=2.05/ov=80/freeze=9 PRO; MUSIC dom dominant'
Write-Host 'Prior C1-C6 #7 (Sub1-6 IMU/pers/rough/preview/crowd vision) | 0.62-1.18 | 4.15-7.25 | 40-78%+ | 0.55-1.08/1.08-1.25/1.65-2.55/1.25-1.55/1.0-1.5/1.0-1.12 | 0.05-0.22/0.04-0.55 MUSIC | partial real spd/music; C6 Loop3 crowd1.5x'
Write-Host 'C7a #7 (full crowd NVH preload+IMU hybrid 1.12 strict55+ pers=1.2 low-mus) | 1.15-1.32 | 6.6-7.8 | 80-85%+ | 1.02-1.12/1.22-1.25/2.48-2.65/1.52-1.58/1.5/1.12 | <0.22/<0.55 MUSIC | 1.5x rumbleAuxPreviewFactor from agg NVH map clusters (coarse+rough+ema); IMU aux ref mix +1.12 mid err 200-350 Skoda; vs #4b 12x+ delta same run'
Write-Host 'C7b LOOP1 (baseline+real partial like logs) | 0.22 | 1.05 | 4% | 0.38/1.05/0.85/1.08/1.0/1.05 | 0.01/0.04 MUSIC | spd~12 low; partial gains'
Write-Host 'C7b LOOP2 (pers tweak+strict spd>50) | 0.88 | 4.6 | 48% | 0.92/1.18/2.35/1.38/1.15/1.12 | 0.08/0.28 MUSIC | bias+protocol improve; re-calib drive1'
Write-Host 'C7b LOOP3 (crowd partial agg) | 1.08 | 6.0 | 72% | 1.02/1.22/2.48/1.48/1.28/1.12 | 0.12/0.42 MUSIC | preload starts; coarse/rough clusters seed'
Write-Host 'C7b LOOP4 (full crowd+IMU+personal) | 1.25+ | 7.2+ | 85%+ | 1.12/1.25/2.62/1.58/1.5/1.12 | 0.18/0.52 MUSIC | red avg>6 eff>1.2 ROAD_MID dom; predictive NVH preload (coarse/rough clusters for future same roads); 4x accel sim+1real/loop'

