# Calibrate strictly to two 2026-06-29 real logs (parsed/confirmed via terminal ls + stats; abs C:\Users\user\AndroidStudioProjects\CarANC\log\anc_session_20260629_173945.log 14MB 96 #7 guided snaps effMidMu avg 0.147 max 1.015, red max 3.954, midScale=1, dominant mostly MUSIC_BROAD, speed avg ~10, music=true, new fields=0; anc_session_20260629_181703.log 10.8MB #7 params mu=2.05/ov=80/freeze=9, 2 ROAD_MID, high bumps, new fields=0).
# Latest f4c00dc: IMU hybrid (rumbleAccelEma + aux ref mix in ReferenceSignalPipeline for preview), personalRumbleBias (apply to rumbleVibBoost on top of tier), roughness/coarse from VehicleSpeedSnapshot/Provider for crowdsourced NVH maps/predictive preload 1.5x aux on agg clusters.
# 2 internal improve-sim cycles:
