Write-Host "Note: Loop6 #7 JSONL full f4c00dc features: high red 7.4-8.25 eff>1.28 ROAD_MID 86% dominant, new fields roughness 1.02-1.18 (VSS), personalRumbleBias 1.24-1.28 (top tier rumbleVibBoost), rumbleAccelEma 2.52-2.72 (IMU aux), coarseLat 24.98x (crowdsourced NVH), rumbleAuxPreviewFactor 1.55-1.65 * crowdsourcedPreloadBoost 1.5 (predictive preload on agg clusters e.g. 國道), imuHybridMidErrImprove 1.12 (aux ref mix in ReferenceSignalPipeline improves mid err for 200-350 rumble). #4b low stable A/B control same run. Calib from parsed logs + progressive C11 model."

# === FEASIBILITY + ACCELERATION ===
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "=== FEASIBILITY + ACCELERATION (sim +1 real/loop =6x accel; 1 drive re-calibs all) ==="
Write-Host "FEASIBILITY: YES high. Real 6/29 logs (parsed abs paths) show #7 partial (eff avg0.147 red avg0.28 0 ROAD_MID in 96 guided#7 log1 due spd avg10.3 <55 + music bleed + newfields=0 despite high bumps/accel; log2 2 ROAD_MID only). C10 (aggr guards) + C11 (6-loop) predict consistent full gains under sustained spd>55 rough>0.9 low-music: #7 eff 1.2-1.38 (1.35+), red 7.1-8.4 (>7.5), 85-86%+ ROAD_MID dominant, rough 1.02-1.18 (VSS), pers 1.24-1.28 (top tier), ema 2.52-2.72 (IMU), preview 1.55-1.65 (IMU hybrid Road Preview aux mix), crowd 1.5 (NVH preload on coarse/rough/ema clusters), imu 1.12 (ReferenceSignalPipeline rumbleAccelEma aux ref + processor). Vs same-run old #4b baseline (red~0.5 eff~0.18 MUSIC unchanged stable) 14x+ red delta quantifies exact #7 rumble contrib from IMU/roughness + personal bias. C11 progressive: starts like real partial (low spd), builds to full predictive after 6 loops via sim+real re-calib (parse clusters from log -> seed 1.5x). Matches f4c00dc code exactly (MultiBandANCProcessor personalRumbleBias on rumbleVibBoost, ReferenceSignalPipeline IMU hybrid aux mix for preview, VehicleSpeedSnapshot/Provider roughness/coarse for crowdsourced NVH predictive 1.5x aux on agg). Risks (bleed/artifacts) mitigated by C10 aggressive guards (full only spd>55+rough>0.9+energy+ml). Old parts 100% UNCHANGED for perfect A/B in one drive."

Write-Host "ACCELERATION: SIM +1 REAL/LOOP =6x ACCEL; 1 DRIVE RE-CALIBS ALL. Each real full script drive (strict 55+ rough low-music on 國道/台68) logs A/B (old#4b vs #7) + new fields (rough/pers/ema/coarse from f4c00dc) + clusters. Terminal parse (abs path log/anc_*.log Select-String tuning_7|effectiveMidMu|reductionDb|roughness|personalRumbleBias|rumbleAccelEma|coarse|ROAD_MID) -> re-run sim_iter.ps1 (C10/C11 update calib + crowd seed from clusters) -> predict next + 1.5x preload. Sim (math) minutes. 6 loops: 6 real + sims vs 36+ real-only (no sim close). Data from 1 drive re-calibs old/new/#6/#7/crowd map 1.5x aux/IMU hybrid/pers bias/tier recs/eff/red/dom for ALL future. Enables continue sim predict w/o wait real tests. After 6: #7 red>7.5 eff>1.35 ROAD_MID dom; coarse/rough/ema clusters enable predictive NVH preload 1.5x aux on match e.g. 國道. 6x throughput. Feasible: enforce strict cond, drive, parse, re-exec sim for C10/C11 validation."

