Write-Host "1. In AncTestScript.kt finish / tuning_finish: add 'EXPORT: after drive terminal parse abs C:\Users\user\AndroidStudioProjects\CarANC\log\anc_session_*.log -Pattern \"tuning_7_strong_road|coarseLat|roughness|personalRumbleBias|rumbleAccelEma|reductionDb|ROAD_MID\" | group clusters (coarse ~0.001deg + rough>0.9 + ema>2.3 + red>4) -> local NVH map json (privacy). Future #7 on match e.g. 國道 auto preload rumbleAuxPreviewFactor *1.5 predictive (crowdsourced from prior #7 coarse/rough/ema clusters). Log scenario \"export coarse/rough/ema clusters for crowdsourced NVH map preload 1.5x; in #7 log rough clusters for predictive 1.5x aux on match e.g. 國道\" + spectrum 200-350Hz red.'"
Write-Host "2. In #7 instr tuning_7_strong_road: add 'STRICT sustained spd>55 kmh rough (國道/台68 high bumps) low-music<15% pers=1.25 tier=PRO; LOG rough clusters (coarse GPS + roughness + rumbleAccelEma from VehicleSpeedSnapshot + ReferenceSignalPipeline) for predictive NVH preload 1.5x aux on same road match. Monitor running_snapshot: rumbleAuxPreviewFactor crowdsourcedPreloadBoost imuHybridMidErrImprove roughness personalRumbleBias rumbleAccelEma coarse* energyFactor. If spd<55 during #7 -> WARN partial (real 6/29 log1 spd~10 limited); repeat for full C10/C11 data + crowd clusters.'"
